headline: NetApp (NasdaqGS:NTAP) Slides 22% Following Revenue Forecast Impact
summary: NetApp (NasdaqGS:NTAP) experienced a significant stock decline of 22% over the last week, a movement that coincides with the company's latest announcement outlining its fourth quarter and full fiscal year 2025 guidance. The expected net revenues and earnings per share are specific forecasts that often prompt market reactions. Meanwhile, the broader market showed volatility as concerns over tariffs and an economic slowdown contributed to a 3% fall for the Nasdaq Composite. When understanding...
